$$\displaystyle 
A \cup B =
  \{ \omega \in \Omega: 
		(\omega \in A)
		 \vee 
		(\omega \in B) \}
$$

If $$A_1, A_2, ...$$ is a [[Sequence]] of [[sets|Set]], then:

$$\displaystyle
\bigcup_{i=1}^{\infty}A_i = 
	\{\omega \in \Omega:
	  \omega \in A_i
		\text{for at least one i}\}
$$